In all seriousness though, I do want you to ask yourself: when’s the last time you were able to sit down and intensely pay attention to one task for a long time?

00:00:21.500 --> 00:00:26.220
If you’re anything like me, this has become
harder and harder to do as we’ve added more
distractions to our lives –

00:00:26.220 --> 00:00:34.180
tweets, snaps, messages, browser tabs, cookies
that must be clicked – they’re in endless supply,
while your brain’s ability to resist them is, sadly, not.

00:00:34.180 --> 00:00:37.360
So that’s why today we’re turning our
